headline: Linde Publishes 2024 Sustainable Development Report
summary: WOKING, England, June 20, 2025--Linde (Nasdaq: LIN) announced today it has published its 2024 Sustainable Development Report, outlining the company's progress towards meeting its sustainability goals.
